# Prompts

New or changed **LLM system prompts**, instruction blocks, or reusable agent text for this repo should live under **`backend/app/prompts/`** (e.g. extend `study_chat.py` or add a small module there). Avoid scattering long prompt strings in routers or services—**import** from `app.prompts` instead.
